    subHeader: "",
    contentHeader: 'New Year Healthy Getaway',
    content: "<p class='first'>2023 is all about self-care and wellness. How about planning a healthy getaway? There are many options to choose from around the world. From tropical paradises to mountainous retreats, each country offers a unique set of features that can contribute to a rejuvenating and restorative vacation.</p><p>Some popular destinations for a healthy getaway include countries known for their spa culture or stunning natural scenery and outdoor activities. Others focus on wellness and mindfulness. Each of these countries offers a variety of options for healthy living, including fitness, nutrition, and stress-reduction activities.</p><p>In this article, we will take a closer look at some of the top countries for a healthy getaway and what they offer. Ready for a rejuvenation journey?</p><a href='https://shawellnessclinic.com/en' target='_blank' class='underline font-bold'>SHA Wellness Clinic – Spain</a> (With a new location in Mexico opening in 2023)<div class='py-4'><img src='/images/newYearHealtyGetaway-1.jpg'class='object-cover h-[400px] block m-auto'/><p class='text-center text-sm'>Source: Conde Nast Traveller</p></div><p>Overlooking the Mediterranean Sea, SHA Wellness Clinic offers world-class treatments and focuses on specific things such as weight loss, fitness training, anti-smoking and cognition-based plans. Unlike the other locations, SHA Wellness is a clinical health facility. They also offer an Immune System program focusing on building a strong immunity system for your body and helping you fight any viruses you might face during the year.</p><p>Ready to book a suitable program for your needs? Choose SHA Wellness Clinic!</p><a href='https://www.anandaspa.com/' target='_blank' class='underline font-bold'>Ananda Spa – Himalayas, India</a><div class='py-4'><img src='/images/newYearHealtyGetaway-2.jpg' class='object-cover h-[400px] block m-auto'/><p class='text-center text-sm'>Source: Healing Hotels of the World</p></div><p>Known as the 'Spiritual Pathway,' Ananda Spa offers a stress management program. Start your year without stress and with proper stress management practices by enjoying a peaceful getaway in the Himalayas. From therapeutic activities such as yoga, meditation, breath regulation, and tailored therapies, Ananda Spa is ready to welcome you on a memorable spiritual journey.</p><p>Enjoy a wonderful getaway amidst the Himalayan Forest, and get ready to come back fully refreshed and rejuvenated!</p><a href='https://www.liphe.me/' target='_blank' class='underline font-bold'>LipHe Wellness Retreat – Lebanon</a><div class='py-4'><img src='/images/newYearHealtyGetaway-3.jpg'class='object-cover h-[400px] block m-auto'/><p class='text-center text-sm'>Source: Spa Opportunities/Tom Walker</p></div><p>LipHe is tucked away among the pine and olive trees of North Lebanon, a wellness retreat dedicated to promoting a natural and balanced lifestyle.</p><p>It offers various services and amenities to its guests as massages, an infrared sauna, yoga and aqua gym sessions, and an outdoor pool. Nutritional microscopy is offered as part of a health coaching consultation based on your blood composition. A healthy plant-based diet, as well as an alkaline diet, is provided.</p><div class='py-4'><img src='/images/newYearHealtyGetaway-4.jpg'class='object-cover h-[400px] block m-auto'/><p class='text-center text-sm'>Source: Trip Advisor</p></div><p>Stay away from the buzz of life’s never-ending chaos and cleanse your body of all external toxins.</p><a href='https://nayarasprings.com/' target='_blank' class='underline font-bold'>Nayara Springs, Pura Vida – Costa Rica</a><p>Located amidst the flora and fauna, Pura Vida is a chic getaway away from all distractions. Relax with morning yoga, meditation, spa treatments, the traditional volcanic mud treatment, and a cleansing detox treatment with volcanic mud. Experience the wonders of nature and immerse your senses in a remarkable adventure in the forest.</p><div class='py-4'><img src='/images/newYearHealtyGetaway-5.jpg'class='object-cover h-[400px] block m-auto'/><p class='text-center text-sm'>Source: Costa Rica Experts</p></div><p>Volcanic mud is highly mineral-rich, making it ideally suited for exfoliating and treating inflammations of the skin and joints.</p><p>Pamper yourself and book that vacation!</p><a href='https://wakayaresort.com/' target='_blank' class='underline font-bold'>Wakaya Club & Spa – Fiji</a><div class='py-4'><img src='/images/newYearHealtyGetaway-6.jpg'class='object-cover h-[400px] block m-auto'/><p class='text-center text-sm'>Source: Wakaya Resort Website</p></div><p>Powered by Fiji’s well known natural healing powers, the Wakaya Club & Spa is the ideal location to enjoy a holistic getaway in 2023. It offers its visitors an unforgettable experience by exploring the splendid island with nature walks and enjoying remarkable holistic activities and adventures such as snorkeling, stand up paddleboarding and swimming in the pool.</p><div class='py-4'><img src='/images/newYearHealtyGetaway-7.jpg'class='object-cover h-[400px] block m-auto'/><p class='text-center text-sm'>Source: Wakaya Resort Website</p></div><p>During your stay, you can enjoy a magnificent spa experience through various services offered and get the chance to try on exceptional oils using local ingredients. If you’re wondering about the type of food offered, all meals are prepared using local and fresh ingredients. It is categorized into Farm to table and Ocean to table depending on your preferences.</p>",
    month: "JAN 2023 EDITION",
    img: "/images/newYearHealtyGetaway.jpg",
    author: "Yara Arkadan",
    topics: ["TRAVEL", "WEEKEND GETAWAYS"],
    theme: "",
    date: "January 01, 2023",
    template: 2,
