    mainHeader: `Beyonce's performance in Dubai`,
    subHeader: "",
    contentHeader: 'Beyoncé Shines in a Spectacular Performance at a Private Event in Dubai',
    content: "<p class='first'>After 4 years of not performing, Beyonce made an exclusive and successful appearance at the grand reveal of Dubai’s luxury hotel Atlantis the Royale on January 21, 2023. The concert took place at a private event attended by around 1,500 guests including Kendall Jenner, Nia Long, Liam Payne, Ashley Park, Jay-Z, and many influencers from the region and public figures.</p><p>According to reports, Queen Beyonce earned $24 million for her performance. As it was a private event, the performance was supposed to be kept a secret. In this digital age, one cannot pretend anything is a secret... especially when the most loved Queen Beyonce is sharing the stage with Blue Ivy.</p><p>Throughout the night, Lebanese talent was evident – and I couldn’t be prouder. First, the star of the show wore a custom-made dress by Lebanese designer Nicolas Jebran.<div><a href='https://www.instagram.com/p/Cnt4KJJoUTY/?igshid=YWJhMjlhZTc%3D' target='_blank'><img src='/images/beyonceInDubai-1.jpg' class='w-[375px] h-[400px] object-cover block m-auto py-2'/></a><p class='text-sm text-center'><a href='https://www.instagram.com/p/Cnt4KJJoUTY/?igshid=YWJhMjlhZTc%3D'>Source:@nicolasjebran</a></p></div><p>With gold sequins and embellished sleeves, the dress was an extravagant red princess-cut gown.</p><p>Also, Beyonce’s incredible performance was accompanied by the outstanding Lebanese dance group Mayyas - the winners of America’s Got Talent. A song by the well-known Lebanese singer Fairuz was also played during one of the performances.</p><div><a href='https://www.instagram.com/p/CnzJVLHszT7/?igshid=YWJhMjlhZTc%3D' target='_blank'><img src='/images/beyonceInDubai-2.jpg' class='w-[375px] h-[400px] object-cover block m-auto py-2'/></a><p class='text-sm text-center'><a href='https://www.instagram.com/p/CnzJVLHszT7/?igshid=YWJhMjlhZTc%3D'>Source:@mayyasoffiacial</a></p></div><p>The event was a one-of-a-kind experience, leaving attendees in happy tears and awe! </p>",
    month: "JAN 2023 EDITION",
